I"J<p><strong>Huge dragon, chaotic good</strong></p>

<p><strong>Armor Class</strong> 18 (natural armor)</p>

<p><strong>Hit Points</strong> 172 (15d12+75)</p>

<p><strong>Speed</strong> 40 ft., burrow 40 ft., fly 80 ft.</p>

